summary: The Avengers saying things I overhear at dance 1:
body:
The Avengers saying things I overhear at dance 1:

Peter, May, Pepper, and Tony are watching a movie. Peter’s phone starts ringing during a very important part, and his ringtone is of the Minions singing Darth Vader’s theme

Peter, shocked that he’s actually getting a phone call: OH MY GOD IM SO SORRY I DONT EVER GET PHONE CALLS

Meanwhile Tony is just cracking up over hearing the minions sing Darth Vader’s theme: What on Earth is that?

Pepper, May, and Peter at the same time: How do you not…? ITS THE MINIONS SINGING DARTH VADER’S THEME
